Zambia’s First-Quarter Tax Collection Exceeds Target, Authority Says

-- B y   A n t h o n y   M u k w i t a
-- 
2011-05-20T11:22:01Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-20/zambia-s-first-quarter-tax-collection-exceeds-target-authority-says.html
Zambia’s tax collection in the first
quarter exceeded its target, the Zambia Revenue Authority said
in an e-mailed statement today.  The country collected 3.89 billion kwacha ($818 million),
compared with a target of 3.81 billion kwacha, the Lusaka-based
authority said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Anthony Mukwita in Lusaka at 
 amukwita1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at 
 asguazzin@bloomberg.net  